<div class="title">Still Addicted</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamines (Adderall)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Jennifer&Exact=1">Jennifer</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Jennifer. "Still Addicted: An Experience with Amphetamines (Adderall) (exp32179)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 29, 2004. erowid.org/exp/32179</div>

<br/>



